Product Name: Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker
Product Description:
Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker

Featuring a thermostatically controlled oven, 2 burner hob and independent grill, the Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker is built from stainless steel (ideal for marine environments) and features a stylish glass oven door with locking latch to stop the door opening, even on rough waters!

The Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker can be mounted for a fixed installtion on a flat surface or secured using the gimballed mounting brackets supplied for an adjustable installation solution. For added safety the Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker comes with a set of adjustable pan holders to secure two pans safely on the hob (perfect against the momentum of water!) as well as flame failure devices.

Please note: There are two different models of the Spinflo Nelson Cooker, with this particular model being optimised specifically for marine use thanks to the addition of the Sea Rail Pan Clamps to keep pans secure whilst on the water. For the standard Spinflo Nelson Cooker (for caravans and motorhomes) please click here.

Spinflo Nelson 2 Burner Hob Marine Cooker features

  • Two Burners
  • Thermostatically controlled oven
  • Powerful independent grill
  • Flame Failure Safety Cut Outs on all burners
  • Can be used with either butane or propane gas
  • Gimballed mounts
  • Pan Support
  • Pan Clamps (Sea Rails)
  • Oven Shelf
  • Door safety latch to stop the door opening while cruising
  • Grill Pan
  • Baking Tray
  • Roasting Tin
  • Grill Pan Cradle
  • Dimensions H525 x W484 x D420 mm

Product Name: Fiamma F65 F80 Campervan and Motorhome Awning Privacy Room
Product Description:
Fiamma F65 and F80 Motorhome Awning Privacy Room

A special version of the Fiamma Awning Privacy Room designed for use with Roof Mounted Awning Canopies and specially designed panels for vehicles such as the Fiat Ducato, Citroen Relay and Peugoet Boxer which enables for transformation of the F65S Fiamma Awnings into a functional living room or bedroom!

Offering improved protection against the elements as well as providing a peaceful and concealed space of solitude in the great outdoors, the Fiamma F65 and F80 Privacy Room features the easy to use clip system for a quicker and more straightforward installation and stylish qualities such as mosquito mesh panes, curtains and clear vinyl windows.

The Fiamma F65 and F80 Privacy Room is easily adjustable, making it versatile for changeable weather including windows which can be quickly rolled up to reveal mosquito panels for warmer days and walls which can be used independently or inclusively, providing limited or total protection depending on the weather.

Additional zip panels of 20, 40, 70, 100, 125 and 150 lengths are available to enlarge the front panel of the Privacy Room so as to fit awnings up to 450cm length

Stylish, quiet and efficient mini bar fridge

Product Name: Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide
Product Description:
Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide

Left or right hand curved 7ft-6 swimming pool slide with steps and stainless steel handrails

A classic swimming pool slide design perfect for family fun, the Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide is blue as standard, however can be customised with your own personal colour for an additional 10%. Suitable for a minimum suggested pool depth of 3ft 6, the Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide also comes supplied with a water jet kit which can be fed either by a hose pipe or via a connection to the swimming pool pump.

If you're planning to concrete the Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide into a permanent position then anchors aren't needed, however anchors will need to be purchased should the pool slide ever need to be moved for any reason.

For more information and enquiries regarding the Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide, please give our team a call on 0151 334 0222 and ask for John. 

Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide features

  • Standard blue curved swimming pool slides are usually sent within 7 days
  • Personal, customised colours of the curved swimming pool water slide tend to be sent within 10 approximate days
  • Comes Standard with Fibreglass Steps and Support
  • You will need two stainless steel deck anchors for safety reasons.
  • Shipping is normally priced somewhere between £85 and £110
  • Please note: The Curved Swimming Pool Water Slide is not suitable for commercial use.

Product Name: 12ft Steel Pro MaxSteel Frame Above Ground Swimming pool
Product Description:
This page to be updated shortly with the new Bestway Pro Max above ground steel frame pool

 

12ft Metal Frame Above Ground Garden Pool Set

An affordable and robust above ground swimming pool which is also quick and easy to set up, the 12ft Steel Pro Metal Frame Garden Pool Set is an ideal family swimming pool perfect for Summer parties, keeping cool on hot days, luxurious relaxation and for fun with friends and family!

Unlike permanent swimming pools which require lots of work, digging, time and expense, the 12ft Steel Pro Metal Frame Garden Pool Set requires hardly any time or hard work to set up, only requiring a flat, solid surface for installation and when you’re done the metal frame pool set can be simply taken down and packed away.

How do I put the 12ft Steel Pro Metal Frame Garden Pool Set together?

Steel frames are at the heart of the 12ft Garden Pool Set and are fitted together using simple ‘T’ connectors and ‘C’ clips which are then used to hold the liner and durable outer wall in place (which flaps over the sides a little to protect against rust or injury!). The only time you’ll ever need to wield a screwdriver is whilst fitting the filter pump, which in itself is pretty straightforward.

It’s pretty much as simple as that and usually takes no more than an hour to construct, so you can spend less time building and more time splashing about in your very own pool! To give you an extra helping hand, the 12ft Steel Pro Metal Frame Garden Pool Set comes with a handy set-up and maintenance DVD for some simple pointers.

12ft Steel Pro Metal Frame Garden Pool Set features

  • Heavy gauge 3 layer PVC side walls
  • Rust resistant frame
  • Convenient drain plug (for easy draining!)
  • Filter pump
  • Installation & maintenance guide DVD
  • Quick and easy set up

Product Name: Solar Panel Mounting Brackets
Product Description:
Solar Panel Mount Brackets

These solar panel brackets can be used with aluminium frame solar panels providing a stable fixing for caravan and marine applications. Both the corner and side mounts raise the solar panels to the ideal height above the surface of the vehicle providing ventilation below and highest efficiency possible.

The perfect fixing method for caravans and boats (no need to drill holes)

Solar panel glue mounted brackets are the ideal way to fix solar panels onto the roof or deck of motorhomes, caravans and boats. The mounts can be safely bonded to the surface ideally with Sikaflex 221. Acting as wind deflectors they maintain the gap between the solar panel & the roof top or deck. The corner mounts are sold as a set of four with the side brackets available as a pair.

Specifications

  • Dimensions:
    • Corners - 150mm x 150mm x 65mm
    • Side - 180mm x 120mm x 60mm
  • For aluminium framed solar panels
  • Larger panels 80w and above require additional side mounting brackets
  • Available in Black or White ABS plastic
  • Recommended adhesive Sikaflex 221

Installation

The brackets are screwed or bolted to the solar unit using stainless steel self-tapping screws. Once the brackets are attached to the panel its ready to be glued to the roof surface or deck using Sikaflex 221, other glues may not be strong or weather proof enough.

  • Strong vibration and impact resistance for long-term durability
  • Bonds metals, plastics, composites, and more

Product Name: Victron BlueSolar MPPT Leisure Battery Charge Controller
Option Set: Victron Energy BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller
Product Description:
Victron BlueSolar MPPT Leisure Battery Charge Controller

The Victron BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller is a device that maximizes the energy harvest from your solar panels and stores it efficiently in your batteries. It uses the latest and fastest technology to achieve a full charge in the shortest possible time, while also extending the life of your batteries. The BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller is available in various models with varying voltage and current capacities to suit your power needs. Victron’s BlueSolar couldn’t be easier to install and can be configured for different battery types. The Victron BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller is a powerful and versatile device that can significantly improve the performance of your solar system. It is a great option for anyone who wants to maximize their solar energy production and extend the life of their batteries.

The Victron BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller maximizes your solar energy harvest with Ultra-Fast Maximum Power Point Tracking, ensuring every bit of power is collected from your panels. This can significantly boost efficiency compared to traditional controllers. To protect your batteries, BatteryLife intelligently adjusts settings to ensure a full recharge at least once a week, extending their lifespan. Finally, you can monitor and control your system remotely using the VictronConnect app with Bluetooth or the Victron Remote Management Portal with an internet connection.

Check out Victron's full solar range here!

Key Features:

  • Maximum Power Point Tracking (MPPT): This technology ensures that every drop of available power is drawn from your solar panels, even in changing light conditions. This can improve energy harvest by up to 30% compared to traditional PWM charge controllers.
  • BatteryLife: Get the most out of your solar panels with ultra-fast MPPT technology. The BlueSolar has intelligent battery management prevents damage and keeps your batteries healthy. The BlueSolar allows you to configure the exact voltage in which BlueSolar disconnects a load this in turn prevents any excessive drain on your leisure battery. This feature prevents damage to your batteries by automatically adjusting the load disconnect voltage to ensure a full recharge at least once a week.
  • Remote Control and Monitoring: You can monitor and control your BlueSolar MPPT Charge Controller remotely using the VictronConnect app with a Bluetooth dongle, or through the Victron Remote Management Portal (VRM) with an internet connection - both services are free of charge to use, letting you to easily manage your solar system from anywhere without any additional cost.

Product Description:
Thetford C402C Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet

A caravan and motorhome cassette toilet with several unique features for ease of use and convenience

Featuring a waste tank with wheels and retractable handle for complete ease of handling, the Thetford C402 Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet also has a handy waste tank level indicator as well as an in built emptying spout and vent plunger for emptying without splashing.

A lightweight yet robust design with an optimal use of space, the Thetford C402 Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet comes complete with an automatic pressure release valve which prevents a build up of gases in the waste holding tank to reduce odours.

  • Full waste tank indicator
  • Removable mechanism
  • Vent plunger for easy emptying without splashing
  • Powerful flushing system
  • Integral 15 litre water tank, fills through the access door via a retractable filler trough
  • Automatic pressure release vent
  • In built emptying spout
  • Lightweight
  • Wheels and retractable handle on waste tank
  • High quality plastic build
  • Space efficient

Please note: The Thetford C402 Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet is available as either a right or left hand model. Please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to confirm your choice of purchase.

Product Description:
Avtex STH3000 Caravan & Motorhome Digital TV Aerial

Combining simplicity with high performance, the Avtex STH3000 Digital TV Aerial is easy to install and features top of the range optimisation to allow for uninterrupted TV viewing in your caravan or motorhome.

With extremely powerful reception capabilities, a high gain 20dB TV aerial, in-built low noise amplifier and integrated 4G filtering (so that modern smart phone signals won’t disturb TV reception) the Avtex STH3000 Digital TV Aerial is designed for optimum performance.

With a flexible suction mount, the Avtex STH3000 Digital TV Aerial can be easily installed free of drilling and mounted inside or outside your caravan or motorhome. For additional durability the Avtex STH3000 Digital TV Aerial also has UV and water resistant housing.

Avtex STH3000 Caravan & Motorhome Digital TV Aerial Features:

  • Directional
  • High gain 20dB TV aerial
  • Reliably powerful reception capability
  • LTE (4G) integrated filtering
  • Built-in low noise amplifier
  • 2 way power source (12V/24V or TV antenna out)
  • Flexible suction mount (similar to GPS windscreen mount)
  • Pole or wall mounting bracket
  • Mount on almost any flat surface (windscreen, window, cab roof)
  • Suitable for indoor or outdoor use
  • UV resistant housing
  • Water resistant

Product Name: Avtex SB270BT 27" Soundbar for Campervan Caravan and Motorhome TV
Product Description:
Avtex SB270BT Sound Bar for 12v Campervan Caravan and Motorhome TV

27 Inch Soundbar & Bluetooth® Speaker

The Avtex SB270BT soundbar and Bluetooth® speaker is perfect for your campervan, caravan and motorhome television! This six speaker driver system is just what you need on your next outdoor leisure trip. This incredible sound bar is the perfect addition to your TV or even as a stand-alone speaker. Simply connect via Bluetooth® to enjoy music wirelessly.

Able to operate on 12V/24V/240V power, allowing you to use this Bluetooth® wireless speaker in your campervan, motorhome, caravan or boat as well as your home! A bracket is included with the SB270BT speaker to be attached to any Avtex TV. To install, simply remove the TV stand (which isn't required when wall mounting) and attach the bracket using the same screw holes that the stand would use. For other TV makes, consult your retailer regarding mounting. 

SB270BT Sound Bar Key Features:

  • Bluetooth® capabilities for wireless music and connection to Bluetooth® television
  • Compact design
  • Six speaker driver system
  • Easy to install and setup
  • Mounting bracket included
  • USB Playback
  • HDMI Arc
  • Coaxial audio in
  • Aux in
  • EQ settings

Truma Ultrastore BGE 10 Gas & Electric Caravan 10 Litre Water Heater Kit
Product Description:
Truma Ultrastore BGE 10 Gas & Electric Caravan 10 Litre Water Heater

The Truma Ultrastore Rapid BGE 10 is a compact, lightweight, and efficient water heater that is perfect for caravans, campervans, and motorhomes. It features a 10-litre stainless-steel water tank, a powerful 1500W gas heater, and an electric heating element that can be switched between 850W and 1300W. The Truma Ultrastore has a short water heating time, a water temperature range of 30°C to 70°C, and is low on gas consumption.

The Truma Ultrastore Rapid BGE is a great choice for those who want to remain off grid, as it can be powered by gas, mains powers and a combination of both so it can be used to heat the water even faster, it can reduce the heat up time from 30 minutes in gas mode to 15 minutes in mixed mode.

The Truma Ultrastore is easy to use, and the control unit allows you to set the desired water temperature anywhere between 30°C and 70°C. The Truma ultrastore boiler is continuously reheated whilst water is drawn.

Overall, the Truma Ultrastore BGE 10 is a great choice for caravans, campervans, and motorhomes that need a reliable and efficient water heater. It is compact, lightweight, easy to use, and has a long lifespan.

Truma Ultrastore Gas & Electric Caravan Water Heater features

  • Capacity: 10 Litres
  • Short water heating times
  • Water temperature range: 30°c to 70°c
  • Stainless steel water tank
  • Powerful 1500w gas heater
  • Economical use of space
  • Low consumption of gas
  • Optional Cowl Extension Kit (Click Here)
  • Complete independence whilst on the move
  • Electric Heating Element is switchable between 850 Watts and 1300 Watts.
  • Please note that the reciprocal connector for mains power is not included, and the existing connector must be removed to wire manually. This does not affect the warranty.
  • This heater now comes with John Guest fittings. (And it's also black, not blue)

Truma Ultrastore Gas & Electric Heater Operation Times:

For 10L water tank

  • Gas only operation approx. 31min
  • Electrical only operation approx. 29min
  • Gas and Electric operation simultaneously approx. 16min

Product Name: Ferno Aquaboard Spinal Immobilisation System
Product Description:
Aquaboard Spinal Immobilisation System

Designed and developed in conjunction with the RLSS UK, the Ferno Aquaboard is a complete Spinal Immobalisation System for swimming pool rescue.

Featuring an innovative design optimised for the efficiency of health practictioners using it as well as the comfort, safety and support of the patient, the Aquaboard Spinal Immobillisation System is designed for supportive recovery of casulties with suspected spinal injuries in swimming pools and leisure centres.

The Aquaboard Spinal Immobilisation System keeps casualties still in the water and then supports recovery on the poolside, with a Neoprene Back Support which easily attaches to the board to prevent the casualty from slippping once strapped in place.

Aquaboard Spinal Immobilisation System Features

  • Instructions for patient positioning printed on the support
  • Innovative design feature allowing for board to float up and under the casualty
  • Colour coded adjustable strapping system
  • Lightweight adjustable head restraint
  • The injured patient can remain on the Aquaboard whilst X-rays take place
  • Concave design helps patient positioning
  • Comes with instructional DVD

Product Name: Ferno Saver Safe Emergency Evacuation Chair
Product Description:
Ferno Saver Safe Emergency Evacuation Chair

An easy to use, reassuringly safe and complete solution for restricted mobility assistance in emergency evacuation situations

Designed to meet the needs of The Equality Act 2010 as well as the Fire Safety Order 2005, the Ferno Saver Safe Evacuation Chair is the complete solution for emergency evacuation procedures. Built to allow for swift and easy manoeuvring in an emergency situation, the Ferno Saver Safe Evacuation Chair glides down stairs easily and smoothly to ensure against the need for heavy lifting or obstructive manual handling.

Ideal for use in multi-storey public buildings such as shopping centres, sport arenas, galleries, offices and care homes, the Ferno Saver Safe Evacuation Chair can be stored on stairwells, ready for use.

Ferno Saver Safe Evacuation Chair features

  • Improved operator control and comfort
  • Easy grip rubber sleeves around upper and lower handles for easy positioning
  • Reassuring for patient safety
  • Adjustable, removable head pad and secure straps to enhance security and comfort
  • Smooth manoeuvrability
  • Wide rear kick stand providing strength and stability on rear castors to prevent tipping
  • Lightweight with compact profile and easy to store
  • Supplied with wall bracket, dust cover and user guidance signage
  • Simple to maintain, clean and replace (with removable seat cover)
  • Designed for easy lateral transfers to another device

MR16 Regulated LED Bulbs 12 Volt Motorhome Caravan Replacement Lamps
Product Description:
MR16 Regulated LED 12 Volt Motorhome Caravan Replacement Bulb

Why should I buy regulated instead of the cheap Ebay LED bulbs?

Our Regulated MR16 LED bulbs will operate safely on any voltage between ten and thirty volts, and last for up to 80,000 hours continuous usage.  Remember, 12v DC only bulbs, will ONLY run safely, and efficiently at exactly 12 Volts, and your leisure battery is rarely exactly 12v.

A fully charged leisure battery is producing 12.7 Volts plus, and a battery when charging, can reach in excess of 14 Volts.  These voltages will very quickly damage un-regulated MR16 LED lights, in some cases burning them out immediately, but in EVERY case, drastically shortening their lifespan.

MR16 LED Lamp Features:

  • MR16 50mm Diameter
  • Warm or Cool light
  • 2.1 Watt power consumption at 12v (mr16 draws 0.175 Amps)
  • 230 Lumen 120 degree beam angle
  • An MR16 can work between 10-30v DC
  • The MR16 led bulb replaces your caravan or motorhome 12v DC halogen lamp up to 20 watts
  • An MR16 LED light can use as little as 10% power compared to your existing halogen lamp
  • Typical MR16 LED bulb life 25,000 to 30,000 hours
  • Bulk discount available
  • MR16 is NOT suitable for use with a dimmer
  • 2 year replacement warranty

Fibre Optic LED Supersafe Sensory Lighting Kit
Product Description:
Fibre Optic LED Supersafe Sensory Lighting Kit

A soothing visual stimulant ideal for use as an aid for adults and children with specific accommodations including autism and intellectual disabilities, the Fibre Optic LED Supersafe Sensory Lighting Kit can also be used as a profoundly calming tool in the treatment of anxiety or sleep disorders in adults and children.

Consisting of polymer fibres in a cracked, clear sleeve which allows light to leak out of the sides, the Fibre Optic LED Supersafe Sensory Lighting Kit produces a visually stimulating sparkle effect and when used with one of the LED light sources produces a gentle colour change for a profoundly soothing and peaceful effect.

Due to the absence of electricity, the fibre optic strands of the LED Sensory Lighting Kit are completely safe to touch (only carrying light) and also certified phthalate free.

Product Name: Thetford Cassette Toilet and Porta Potti Bottom Tank Cleaner Caravan Motorhome
Product Description:
Thetford Toilet Cassette and Bottom Tank Cleaner (1 Litre)

Thetford Cassette Tank Cleaner is a powerful cleaning agent that cleans the inside of all Thetford toilet waste holding tanks. The Cassette/Bottom Tank Cleaner not only freshens up your tank, it removes stubborn calcium deposits that collect on moving parts and on the tank walls. Thetford Cassette Toilet Tank Cleaner has been specially developed for the periodic extra cleaning and maintenance of your Thetford Porta Potti toilets waste holding tank, for both the cassette caravan/motorhome range and regular camping toilets range.

Once you've finished your holiday clean the waste-holding tank with Thetford Cassette Tank Cleaner.

If you clean the tank regularly, the moving parts will keep functioning properly providing a longer product life. Tip 300ml Cassette Tank Cleaner into a rinsed out tank and fill it with approximately 5L of lukewarm water (works better). Shake the tank back and forth then leave it for at least 24 hours. After emptying, your waste-holding tank will be as good as new. Allow the tank to dry by leaving the blade open. Using Thetford Cassette Tank Cleaner before you store your camper, caravan or camping toilet for longer periods gives you a fresh start at the beginning of a new camping season.

Tip

Put the Thetford cleaner in the tank before your journey home, the movement of your vehicle will do the job of cleaning for you!

Benefits

  • By far the best waste-holding tank cleaning agent
  • Prolongs tank life
  • No scrubbing!
  • Removes deposits easily
  • Leaves behind a pleasant, clean scent
  • Recommended use 2 to 3 times per year
